# 📸 Responsive Image Gallery  

This is a **responsive image gallery** with a **lightbox effect**.  
Users can click on an image to view it in **full-screen mode**.  

## 🛠️ Built With  

This project is developed using:  

- **HTML** - Structure of the gallery.  
- **CSS** - For Styling.  
- **JavaScript** - Lightbox functionality.  


## 🎯 Features  

✔️ **Responsive Design** - Works perfectly on all devices.  
✔️ **Lightbox Effect** - Click on an image to enlarge it.  
✔️ **Smooth Animations** - Uses CSS transitions for better UX.   
 

